<F P=100> United States &amp; Canada </F>
<H3> <TI>   Qian Qichen Meets Canadian Doctor's Widow </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Qian Qichen Meets Canadian Doctor's Widow </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW1504100694 Beijing XINHUA in English 0928 GMT 15 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1504100694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, April 15 (XINHUA) -- Chinese Vice-Premier 
and Foreign Minister Qian Qichen met here this morning with Ella 
Endicott, widow of Dr. James Endicott, in the Diaoyutai State 
Guesthouse. 
  Dr. Endicott, a renowned Canadian peace champion, is 
regarded 
as a life-long friend of the Chinese people. 
  Dr. Endicott was born into a missionary family in Leshan 
city, in China's Sichuan Province, in December 1898, and died in 
Toronto, Canada, in November 1993. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

