opening 
ceremony of the Mediterranean traditional Chinese medicine 
center, a project under the cooperation accord. 
  The Chinese Public Health Ministry delegation arrived in the 
south European state on April 9 and will go to Sudan on April 15. 
  During its stay here, the delegation also visited Malta 
University, hospitals and other medical institutions. 

