<F P=100> HONG KONG &amp; MACAO </F>
<F P=101> Macao </F>
<H3> <TI>   Macao Exhibition of Mainland's Universities Closes </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Macao Exhibition of Mainland's Universities Closes </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW1304112694 Beijing XINHUA in English 0846 GMT 13 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1304112694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Macao, April 13 (XINHUA) -- A five-day exhibition 
about the universities and colleges from China's mainland closed 
here today. 
  Contents of the exhibition cover teaching programs, contents 
of courses and general situations of the mainland's universities. 
