<H3> <TI>   Shandong's Yantai City Elects New Party Secretary </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shandong's Yantai City Elects New Party Secretary </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1704060094 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 16 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK1704060094 </F>
<F P=104>  Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The eighth Yantai city party congress ended on 16 
April. At the first plenary session of the eighth city party 
committee, Du Shicheng was elected secretary of the city party 
committee. 

</TEXT>

