  [Text] Cairo, April 16 (XINHUA) -- Egyptian Foreign 
Minister 'Amr Musa has stressed that President Husni Mubarak's 
visit to China between April 21 and 23 derives its importance 
from the role China has been playing in Asia and other parts of 
the world. 
  Today's Egyptian newspaper "AL-AKHBAR" reported the foreign 
